comments.body:
Why not write it this like?
```
#define detail_LogIfCategoryAndLevelEnabled(category, level, ...)  
    do {                
        Assume(level < BCLog::Level::Info);                                             
        if (LogAcceptCategory((category), (level))) {
            LogPrintLevel_(category, level, false, __VA_ARGS__);
        }                                                            
    } while (0)
```

